<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirmation Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .code {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #d35400;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Confirmation Required</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>We have sent you a token and a session ID that must be confirmed to proceed. Please use the following details to complete your verification:</p>

    <p><strong>Token:</strong></p>
    <div class="code"><%= token %></div>

    <p><strong>Session ID:</strong></p>
    <div class="code"><%= sessionId %></div>

    <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email or contact our support team.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p><strong>Your Company Name</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>